      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのおかげで\n本番も頑張れました",
      "startTime": 7.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 11.966666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ライブもかなり盛り上がったし……\n本当に、ありがとうございました",
      "startTime": 11.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ\n私を言いくるめるやり方は無茶苦茶でしたけどね？",
      "startTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 20.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "無茶苦茶……か",
      "startTime": 20.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "何がおかしいんですか？",
      "startTime": 22.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……実は、麻奈ともライブ前に\n同じようなことをしたな、って思い出して",
      "startTime": 27.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 30.233333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　お姉ちゃんが？",
      "startTime": 30.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、星見まつりに出演した時の話なんだけどな",
      "startTime": 33.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "それって……『星降る奇跡』の日のことですか？",
      "startTime": 37.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 41.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。「屋台を手伝いたい。ダメだったら\nお面をかぶってライブに出る」なんて脅されて……",
      "startTime": 46.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "結局お面をかぶってかき氷を売ったんだよ\nバレないかとヒヤヒヤしたなぁ……",
      "startTime": 54.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 57.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……お姉ちゃんらしいですね",
      "startTime": 57.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 61.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんのことだから、きっとお祭りのために\n何かしたいーなんて言ったんじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 64.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……当たりだ\nさすがによく分かってるな",
      "startTime": 70.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 72.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前ですけど……まだまだいるんですよね\n{user}さんの思い出には……",
      "startTime": 77.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 79.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "私の知らない……お姉ちゃんが",
      "startTime": 79.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……",
      "startTime": 83.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 84.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんとの思い出、もっと聞かせてくれませんか？",
      "startTime": 84.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fireworks-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 88.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "花火……上がりましたね\nあ……っ",
      "startTime": 88.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 94.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばこのイベント\n終演後に上がる花火が見どころ……って聞きました",
      "startTime": 96.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fireworks-01.m4a",
